  <brief_title>Comparison of Oxford UKA and Sigma UKA With RSA.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Oxford Unicompartmental Knee Prosthesis With the Sigma High Performance Partial Knee Using Rontgen Stereophotogrammetric Analysis in Patients With Primary Medial Unicompartmental Knee Osteoarthritis.</official_title>
